name: DU, Push press, rope climb
description:
1 round of:
150 double-unders
30 push presses, ½ body weight
6 legless rope climbs, 15 ft.

Then, 2 rounds of:
75 double-unders
15 push presses, ½ body weight
3 legless rope climbs, 15 ft.

Then, 3 rounds of:
50 double-unders
10 push presses, ½ body weight
2 legless rope climbs, 15 ft.

Post time
